     C* Phase A: a bare 'U' (Auto Report Option) line at the top of an
     C* otherwise-ordinary program. Auto Report preprocessing consumes the
     C* U line (no *AUTO constructs to expand) and the program compiles and
     C* runs identically to the same program without the U line.
     U
     FUARDATA  IP  F    80              DISK
     FUAROUT   O   F    132             PRINTER
     IUARDATA      AA
     I                                        1   2   0N
     OUAROUT   D  1
     O                         N         10
